{"id": 666, "genre": 1000, "title": "现代病之你也有错失恐惧症吗？", "description": "错失恐惧症（FOMO，Fear Of Missing Out），即不愿错过社交网络中任何可能关于自己或关于潮流的信息，否则就会感到精神焦虑的一种疾病。", "record_count": 6213, "comment_count": 28, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183825kTmoitwIxgDX7qKH.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-27T00:45:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 565, "title": "现代病之你也有错失恐惧症吗？", "content": "现代病之你也有错失恐惧症吗？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 28968, "content": "早上刷朋友圈一定要翻到前一天晚上看到的那条为止", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183018dK1smDSv4e0JpPMn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 28987, "content": "一条不感兴趣的文章，某几个朋友也转了就会点开来看", "image": "img/option/option/20160608143422pjWy5OS9mHizv6Z4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 28988, "content": "突然热起来的流行语我都是第一批使用者", "image": "img/option/option/201606071934597q9BCUQ5Vv2GApXH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 28997, "content": "如果不是也会迅速去查明意思熟练地用起来", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183019dItrNkj1aGnoWh0T.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 28994, "content": "每天都会上微博刷刷热搜", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182500Ad9z1MZEj8lHor5F.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 28995, "content": "突然大家都喊谁老公了，不看影视剧也要查查他的八卦", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182500uIlQztgxN6iwHJa1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 28998, "content": "会去一个固定的段子手那边看段子和无数整齐的23333", "image": "img/option/option/201607021832565QpliVWdNX7cnhJ1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 29000, "content": "打开群看到上百条记录也会一条条看过来", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193500QCd4oiyAZ8G97T3q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 29001, "content": "离开手机5分钟，超怕刚好有人找", "image": "img/option/option/2016060719350048B2HVNgtyZo67CT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}